dct_title_s: Ordnance Survey of England and Wales: popular edition one-inch map. Stratford on Avon. Sheet 82
dct_description_sm: Revision 1915. Alternate panel title: Ordnance Survey contoured road map of Stratford on Avon. Sheet 82. Relief shown by 50 feet contour intervals and spot elevation. Surveyed in 1880-86.
